      • logInInBackground

        public static void logInInBackground(java.lang.String loginId,
                                     java.lang.String password,
                                     LogInCallback<LCPassport> callback)
        Logs in a passport with a loginId and password. On success, this saves the session to disk, so you can retrieve the currently logged in passport using LCPassport.getCurrentPassport()
        Parameters:
        loginId - The username or email to log in with.
        password - the password
        callback - callback.done(passport, e) is called when the login completes.
